nodes.bodyText:
@jiajunwang Thank you for the offline discussion!
Conclusion: 1. we will do preprocessing in GarbageCollectionStage. We will sacrifice a bit of performance for better code clarity. All garbage collection logic is better to be in 1 class.
2. There is no good way to deal with the situation described in this thread (same job name). We are not expanding the scope of this PR to cover that, and therefore it will be left as a TODO item for now.

